description: Get in touch with the Black Alumni Association of Denison University.
card1Title: "Send us a message"
card1Body: "For general questions about the BAA, membership, events, or how to get involved, reach us at our general inbox. We'll respond as quickly as our volunteer team allows."
card1Email: "info@denisonbaa.org"
card1Note: "General inquiries · Membership · Events"
card2Title: "Reach the President"
card2Body: "For matters requiring direct executive attention — partnerships, institutional questions, media, or urgent organizational matters — contact the BAA President directly."
card2Email: "president@denisonbaa.org"
card2Note: "Partnerships · Institutional matters · Media"
