      </div>
      <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc8ss6e6pSmA1IvAkPTCJJ5epzHBNtyZBaH6bw0boxOB5vLnA/viewform" class="quick-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Access Resources</a>
